    "body" : "<p>Cucumber does not support hooks on feature levels like specflow having @BeforeFeature and @AfterFeature tags. This is open issue <a href=\"https://github.com/cucumber/cucumber-jvm/issues/515\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">https://github.com/cucumber/cucumber-jvm/issues/515</a></p>\n"
